lity accumulated 179,442 shares. Cibc Mkts holds 0.35% or 901,014 shares in its portfolio. 2,802 are held by Sei Invs Company. Investors use this ratio to decide what multiple of earnings a share is worth.Among 14 analysts covering First American Financial (NYSE:FAF), 7 have Buy rating, 1 Sell and 6 Hold. Therefore 39% are positive. The firm has "Buy" rating by Jefferies given on Monday, December 7. The stock has "Outperform" rating by Credit Suisse on Friday, May 26. BIRD ROGER sold $72,069 worth of stock or 1,601 shares. As per Monday, January 30, the company rating was downgraded by Mizuho. JP Morgan initiated TIER REIT Inc (NYSE:TIER) rating on Thursday, June 2. The firm has "Buy" rating given on Friday, July 21 by Gabelli.Abbott Laboratories (ABT) has an Analysts' Mean Recommendation of 1.9, according to data compiled by Finviz. Abbott Laboratories comprises about 1.0% of Hochman Cole Investment Advisors portfolio, making the share its 29th largest stake. Abbott Laboratories P/E (price to earnings) ratio is 55.94 and Forward P/E ratio of 18.16. Therefore 64% are positive.
